  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ponekad vidite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">w</span> na početku sloga. To nisu inicijalna slova. Zamislite ih kao posebne pravopisne oznake koje određuju granice slogova i čine da su slogovi lakši za čitanje.</p>\n<p>Pravila za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> su:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ako <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> se koristi kao slog, dodajte <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> pre njega: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yi</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ukoliko silaba počinje sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, promenite u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span>. Primeri: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ia</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ya</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ie</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ye</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iao</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yao</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iou</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">you</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iang</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yang</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako se <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ü</span> koristi kao slog, dodajte <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> ispred njega i uklonite tačku: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ü</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yu</span>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yang</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yāng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">央</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yáng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">羊</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yǎng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">养</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yàng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">样</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
